      "title": "Wall-crossing from supersymmetric galaxies",
      "abstract": "We give an elementary physical derivation of the Kontsevich-Soibelman wall crossing formula, valid for any theory with a 4d N = 2 supergravity description. Our argument leads to a slight generalization of the formula, which relates monodromy to the BPS spectrum."
